<template>
  <HeaderMainPage />

  <FillerTemplate v-for="user in users" :key="user" v-bind="user" />




</template>


<script>

import HeaderMainPage from "@/components/HeaderMainPage.vue";
import FillerTemplate from "@/components/FillerTemplate.vue";

export default {
  el: "#FillerTest",
  name: "filler",
  components: {
    HeaderMainPage,
    FillerTemplate
  },
  data() {
    return {
      users: []
      // publications: {
      //   comments: [],
      //   users: []
      // }

    }
  },
  async created() {
    const postId = this.$route.params.id;
    fetch("http://localhost:3000/api/users/" + postId)
      .then((response) => response.json())
      .then(data => {
        this.user = data

        console.table(this.user);



      })

  },
}



</script>

<style scoped>
</style>
